<div class="container">
  <div class="page-navigation">
    <a href="/"><i class="fa fa-home" aria-hidden="true"></i>HOME</a><i class="fa fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i>

    <a href="/home/list_lip2/봄 브라이트">립 추천</a><i class="fa fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i>

    <a href="/home/list_lip2/<%=@product.season%>"><%=@product.season%></a><i class="fa fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i>
    주문하기
  </div>

  <div style="background-color:#ffffff;">
    <hr style="border: solid 1.0px;color:#333333">
    <p align="center" style="margin-bottom:20px; font-size:16px;color:#000000"><strong>주문하기</strong></p>
    <hr style="border: solid 1.0px;color:#333333">
  </div>

  <!--상품정보 출력-->
  <form id="myForm" style="margin-top:40px" action="/home/order_submit" method="post" data-toggle="validator">

  <div class="media panel-body container" style="border: solid 2.0px lightgray; margin-top:20px;padding:0;">
    <div class="pull-left user-info" href="#" float="left" >
      <img class="example" src="https://s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/palette160829111/product/<%=@product.image%>-min.JPG" style="width:140px;height:auto;">
      <br>
    </div>
    <div class="media-body">
      <input type="hidden" name="product_brand" value="<%=@product.brand%>">
      <input type="hidden" name="product_name" value="<%=@product.name%>">
      <input type="hidden" name="product_price" value="<%=@product.price%>">
      <p>[<%=@product.brand %>] <strong><%=@product.name %></strong></p>
      <p style="margin-bottom:20px;"><%=@product.size %> / <%=@product.season%></p>
      <p style="font-weight:bold;">금액:<%=@product.price %>원<span style="color:red;">(배송비 무료)</span></p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div>
    <p class="guarantee">
      본 제품은 해당 브랜드 매장에서 직접 보내드리는 정품입니다. 가품일 시 <strong>10배</strong> 보상해드립니다.
    </p>

    <h4 style="text-align: center;">주문정보 입력</h4>
  </div>

    <div class="form-group">
      <label for="name">이름</label>
      <input type="text" name="name" class="form-control" id="name" data-error="주문자 성함을 입력해주세요." required>
    </div>

    <div class="form-group">
      <label for="tel">연락처</label>
      <input type="text" name="tel" class="form-control" id="tel" data-error="연락처를 입력해주세요." required>
    </div>

    <div class="form-group">

      <label for="address">주소</label>
      <textarea class="form-control" name="address" id="address" rows="5" data-error="주소를 입력해주세요." required></textarea>
    </div>

    <div class="form-group">
      <label for="money_name">입금자 성함</label>
      <input type="text" name="money_name" class="form-control" id="money_name" data-error="입금자 성함을 입력해주세요." required>
    </div>


    <center>
      <button type="submit" class="btn-next" name="product_num" value="<%=@product.image%>">다음</button>
    </center>

  </form>
  <br><br><br>
</div>


<style>
  .btn-next {
    height: 50px;
    width: 200px;
    line-height: 40px;
    display: block;
    margin: 30px auto;
    margin-bottom: 0px;
    color: #ffffff;
    font-size: 14px;
    text-align: center;
    background: #ffaaa3;
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 5px;
  }
  .page-navigation{
    text-align:right;
    margin: 20px 0px 20px 0px;
    color:#56565d;
  }
  .page-navigation>a{
    color:#56565d;
  }
  div.media-body{
    padding-top:20px;
    margin-bottom:20px;
  }
  .guarantee{
    padding:10px;
    text-align:center;
    font-size:12px;
    margin:20px auto;
  }
</style>